                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这是一本产生更多书的书，或者说是一个详备的阅读清单。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="964272342">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-964272342" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-964272342" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="964272342">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/saintini/">恪彥</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-10-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">清晰的将西方文脉梳理在读者面前.不但有着导论影响,更能强烈激发起读者(至少是我)对于阅读西方经典的欲望.</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="524768298">
