            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12050522/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12050522/" class="">第2页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/laurel-nanr/" class=" " title="laurel">laurel</a>
                (春天分手，秋天就会习惯。)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12050522">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">马克思：古希腊的神话和艺术是人类童年时代的美丽的诗，具有永久性的魅力。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-03-26 20:00</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                马克思：<blockquote><q>古希腊的神话和艺术是人类童年时代的美丽的诗，具有永久性的魅力。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
